    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good summary, but can u go a bit deeper on the labor part? Like, is it actually a proven fact that immigration fills shortages, or is that just a theory people use to justify it? I see a lot of conflicting stuff online about whether it actually helps the economy or just hurts local workers.",
